cdata.name: Transfer
cdata.desc:
Transfer is a new cryptocurrency that will feature a uniquely implemented and decentralized p2p anonymization feature via Proof of Stake protocol extensions. Their decentralized network aims to be a fungible and untraceable digital medium of exchange. Transactions are lightning-fast at just 60 seconds confirmation time.Their main goal is availability on all possible devices and using all kinds of Internet services. Such as email, sms, social networks.

Latest Updates

  1. Cross-Send was done completely custom by infernoman. (Cross-Send allows you to spend Transfercoin where Bitcoin is accepted.)
  2. MAC Wallet Trading. Transfercoin is the first to do this.
  3. Full implementation of secp256k1 for ecdsa sig's.
  4. Dark features working based off of dash 0.12.0. (Stealth addresses, Darksend, Encrypted Messaging, Masternodes)
  5. Staking and Masternodes in the same wallet. (If your running a masternode in your wallet)
  6. Masternodes and Staking in an Android Wallet.
